---
---
<section class="about section" id="about">
  <div class="about__grid container">
    <div class="about__image reveal">
      <img
        src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1550547660-d9450f859349?w=900&q=80&auto=format&fit=crop"
        alt="STACKD kitchen — smash technique"
      />
    </div>
    <div class="about__text reveal">
      <p class="eyebrow">Our Story</p>
      <h2 class="section-title">Made with<br />intent.</h2>
      <p>
        STACKD started with one obsession: the perfect smash burger. We took the
        classic American technique — a ball of fresh beef smashed hard on a
        screaming-hot griddle — and made it our whole identity.
      </p>
      <p>
        No frozen patties. No reheated buns. Every burger is pressed to order,
        crisped at the edges, and stacked the way it was meant to be. Fast
        doesn't have to mean careless.
      </p>
      <div class="about__stats">
        <div class="stat">
          <span class="stat__num">2019</span>
          <span class="stat__label">Est.</span>
        </div>
        <div class="stat">
          <span class="stat__num">100%</span>
          <span class="stat__label">Fresh beef</span>
        </div>
        <div class="stat">
          <span class="stat__num">0</span>
          <span class="stat__label">Freezers</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about__grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 5rem;
    align-items: center;
  }
  .about__image img {
    width: 100%;
    aspect-ratio: 4/5;
    object-fit: cover;
    border-radius: var(--radius);
  }
  .about__text {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.25rem;
  }
  .about__text p {
    color: var(--muted);
    line-height: 1.8;
    font-size: 1.05rem;
  }
  .about__stats {
    display: flex;
    gap: 2.5rem;
    margin-top: 1rem;
    padding-top: 2rem;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
  }
  .stat { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.25rem; }
  .stat__num {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--accent);
  }
  .stat__label {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--muted);
  }
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .about__grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 2.5rem; }
    .about__image img { aspect-ratio: 16/9; }
  }
</style>
